data.description: This inviting two-story home, featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and a one car garage, is now on the market!!  Over $100,000.00 in recent updates including new windows, paid off solar, new kitchen cabinets and counters, HVAC including heat pump furnace, ensuring modern comfort and energy efficiency.  Fresh painted interiors, tile and a bathroom upgrade add a finishing touch to this property. As you enter the home, the living room greats you with an open floor plan, as the dining room opens into the updated kitchen.  Step outside to discover a charming patio area and backyard opening to a walking path, perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertainment.  Upstairs, the master suite includes a large walk in closet. The bathroom is all remolded with a walk in shower and glass doors for added convenience and privacy.  Located in a peaceful neighborhood, this home offers comfortable and well-maintained living space with an inviting outdoor retreat, making it an excellent choice for prospective buyers.  The outside was painted in 2021 and the roof was replaced in 2019.
